reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fit and easy to put on
reviews.reviewText: I liked the fabric and perfect fit as well as vibrant color

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome & Inexpensive Fix!
reviews.reviewText: This is my second set of these slipcovers. I was ready for a change in color. I bought another brand and was disappointed in the quality and fit. Looking closely at other brands I could see they didn't fit as well as these, especially around the bottom. They really don't look like slipcovers, which I suppose is the point. What a great and inexpensive way to switch up the look and cover the very worn, flaking faux leather underneath. I washed the old ones and they came out perfect. They're now stored for when I'm ready for the next change.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WOW! If I could give it 10 stars I would!
reviews.reviewText: Wow! I can't believe what a difference these covers make! We were looking for a new kitchen set and I stumbled onto these. For the price, I figured, why not? I'm blown away! They fit like a glove, look fantastic, and can be easily removed and washed. Im picky too - Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Double-up the white
reviews.reviewText: I had two bright, different patterned parson chairs that needed covering. I wanted a neutral white. After reading the reviews about whether the light-colored covers are see-through (yes they are), I bought this 4 pack and doubled them-two per chair. The pattern does not show through and the chairs now look soft, comfortable and a matched set in a bedroom. The fabric is stretchy enough to easily accommodate two covers. Affordable. A quality product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent chair covers!
reviews.reviewText: The orange color is as pictured. The covers are soft and stretchy. They work perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Flimsy stretch material.
reviews.reviewText: Unfortunately, sitting in chair with frequency has caused the fabric to separate along the seams on top of chair and sides. (Note: as a caregiver one person sits in one chair daily since purchased in September). The cover on that chair is splitting on the top and sides from frequent use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these to replace the chair covers I have had for a few years, and they are wonderful. Look nice, fit perfect and comfortable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Nice color and fit. Would prefer it was heavier fabric to look better as fabric slides up from bottom. Better than several I tried in all accounts.
